OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773673868
OL,3,CPM pledges cost of living help after
OL,4,Cresisting Trump's call for warships
OL,6,FSir Keir on Sunday did not heed calls
OL,7,Ffrom Mr Trump to deploy warships to
OL,8,Fsecure the Strait of Hormuz, a key oil
OL,9,Ftrade route in the Middle East being
OL,10,Fblockaded by Iran.
OL,12,FInstead, Britain is currently mulling
OL,13,Fover the possibility of sending mine-
OL,14,Fhunting drones to the region amid
OL,15,Fworries of an Iranian build-up of
OL,16,Fexplosives in the narrow sea passage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
