OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773673868
OL,3,CPM pledges cost of living help after
OL,4,Cresisting Trump's call for warships
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's heating oil
OL,7,Fannouncement on Monday comes after
OL,8,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said Treasury
OL,9,Fofficials have "found the money" to
OL,10,Fhelp the 1.5 million households
OL,11,Frelying on the fuel.
OL,13,FHeating oil is not protected by the
OL,14,Fenergy price cap and its price per
OL,15,Flitre has doubled as a result of the
OL,16,Fstranglehold on oil leaving the Middle
OL,17,FEast since the US-Israeli war with
OL,18,FIran began.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773673868
OL,3,CPM pledges cost of living help after
OL,4,Cresisting Trump's call for warships
OL,6,FInside Downing Street, Sir Keir will
OL,7,Fsay: "It's moments like this that tell
OL,8,Fyou what a Government is about.
OL,10,F"My answer is clear. Whatever
OL,11,Fchallenges lie ahead, this Government
OL,12,Fwill always support working people.
OL,14,F"That is my first instinct ` my first
OL,15,Fpriority ` to help you with the cost
OL,16,Fof living through this crisis."
OL,18,FThe Prime Minister will also raise
OL,19,Fconcerns about claims that suppliers
OL,20,Fof heating oil have cancelled orders
OL,21,Fand then jacked up prices.
OL,26,@oD@FOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
