OL,3,CPM pledges cost of living help after
OL,4,Cresisting Trump's call for warships
OL,6,FSir Keir on Sunday spoke to Mr Trump
OL,7,Ffor the first time since the US
OL,8,Fpresident called for help from other
OL,9,Fnations to secure the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FThe pair "discussed the ongoing
OL,12,Fsituation in the Middle East and the
OL,13,Fimportance of reopening the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz to end the disruption to global
OL,15,Fshipping, which is driving up costs
OL,16,Fworldwide", a Downing Street
OL,17,Fspokeswoman said.
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
