CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773673868
OL,3,CPM pledges cost of living help after
OL,4,Cresisting Trump's call for warships
OL,6,FBut there was no response from the
OL,7,FPrime Minister to the President's call
OL,8,Ffor the UK and other nations impacted
OL,9,Fby the blockade to send warships to
OL,10,Fthe region to protect the Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz.
OL,13,FBritain is "intensively" looking at
OL,14,Fwhat it can do to help reopen the
OL,15,Froute, Mr Miliband said on Sunday.
OL,17,FThe military could send mine-hunting
OL,18,Fdrones to the region, defence sources
OL,19,Fhave said, as the Government seeks to
OL,20,Fstave off criticism from Mr Trump for
OL,21,Fignoring his call for warships.
OL,26,@uD@LOUuD@XO]
